	<h1 class="title"> 3D 打印肝脏不是概念，它就要开始销售了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1741/small/1741.jpg?1435203015" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">高宇馨</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-21 08:27:38 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3740/medium/3740.jpg?1436641661" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="3740" data-title="《 3D 打印肝脏不是概念，它就要开始销售了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3740/medium/3740.jpg?1436641661" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3740.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
